'''''Call to Arms''''' (also known as '''''Conquest''''') is a 1982 [[computer wargame]] published by [[Sirius Software]].

==Gameplay==
''Call to Arms'' is a game in which players can fight opponents in Europe during 1942 or in Scotland during 1750 as a strategy wargame.<ref name="CGW9"/>

